OL,3,CFootball club 'heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cplayers and manager injured by hit-and-
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FIt's understood there was an argument
OL,8,Fin the town centre just before the
OL,9,Fcollision. Pictures from ITV News
OL,10,FCentral.
OL,12,FA football club has said their evening
OL,13,Fended in "complete heartbreak" after a
OL,14,Fhit-and-run in Arnold has left one of
OL,15,Ftheir players "fighting for his life".
OL,17,FIt comes after a man was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of attempted murder after a
OL,19,Fcar crash into multiple pedestrians in
OL,20,Fa Nottinghamshire town centre on
OL,21,FSaturday morning (May 9).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
