OL,3,CFootball club 'heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cplayers and manager injured by hit-and-
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FWoodthorpe Park Rangers FC, issued a
OL,8,Fstatement on X this morning saying
OL,9,Fthat "3 members of our team including
OL,10,Fthe manager was struck by a car in
OL,11,FArnold town centre, this has left one
OL,12,Fof our players fighting for his life
OL,13,Fin hospital."
OL,15,FTwo other men also suffered minor
OL,16,Finjuries. The 40-year-old man arrested
OL,17,Fon Saturday evening remains in police
OL,18,Fcustody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
