OL,3,CFootball club 'heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cplayers and manager injured by hit-and-
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police has said
OL,8,FCounter Terrorism Police are not
OL,9,Finvolved in the investigation.
OL,11,FWoodthorpe Park Rangers, who compete
OL,12,Fin the Nottinghamshire Senior League,
OL,13,Fhad been celebrating their end of
OL,14,Fseason awards before the crash.
OL,16,FThe club's said: "We are hoping and
OL,17,Fpraying for our player who is a much
OL,18,Floved lad by all, we're supporting
OL,19,Feach other the best we can.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
