PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778583777
OL,3,CFootball club 'heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cplayers and manager injured by hit-and-
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,F"We are all struggling right now and
OL,8,Fare asking for privacy and respect so
OL,9,Fwe can get our heads around what has
OL,10,Fhappened, this is a heartbreaking and
OL,11,Fawful time for our club."
OL,13,FBasford United FC, who formerly
OL,14,Fgroundshared with Woodthorpe,
OL,15,Fresponded to the social post saying:
OL,16,F"Thoughts & prayers to everyone
OL,17,F@WoodthorpePark, and we hope this is
OL,18,Fan improving situation."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
